OL,3,CStore owner speaks out after 30%
OL,4,Cincrease in shoplifting in the West
OL,5,CMidlands
OL,7,FThe rate of shoplifting has hit its
OL,8,Fhighest level for two decades
OL,9,Fnationally, with thefts from shops and
OL,10,Fstalls increasing by 28% in 2023.
OL,12,FBut in the West Midlands, there has
OL,13,Fbeen a 30% increase between April and
OL,14,FJune this year- a total of 7,443
OL,15,Foffences.
OL,17,FIn May 2024 alone, West Midlands
OL,18,FPolice recorded 2,532 offences.
