OL,5,CMidlands
OL,7,FShop owners across the region say they
OL,8,Fhave never seen shoplifting offences
OL,9,Fso high.
OL,11,FAmong them is Surinder Josan, who runs
OL,12,Fa family-owned DIY shop in Smethwick.
OL,14,F"There's no way out"
OL,16,FHe says "After decades of being able
OL,17,Fto operate without CCTV we're finally
OL,18,Fhaving to look at putting some system
OL,19,Fin.
