OL,7,F"So I've got two cameras for the front
OL,8,Fof the shop, two or three within the
OL,9,Fshop in different corners and then
OL,10,Fsome throughout the back as well.
OL,12,F"There's no way out we just have to
OL,13,Fbuild it up, every time we lose
OL,14,Fsomething to replace that loss of sale
OL,15,Fwe probably have to sell six or seven,
OL,16,Fat least a dozen of those to cover
OL,17,Fthat loss."
