OL,5,CMidlands
OL,7,FAndrew Goodacre from the British
OL,8,FIndependent Retailers Association,
OL,9,Fwhich aims to support independent
OL,10,Fretail shops, says that the scale of
OL,11,Fshoplifting is like a "pandemic".
OL,13,F"It's been almost a pandemic of crime,
OL,14,Fthe number of types of shop affected
OL,15,Fhas widened, the number of incidents
OL,16,Fhas increased. The amount of stock
OL,17,Ftaken at any one time seems to have
OL,18,Fincreased as well."
