OL,3,CStore owner speaks out after 30%
OL,4,Cincrease in shoplifting in the West
OL,5,CMidlands
OL,7,F"Shoplifting is a blight on our retail
OL,8,Foutlets, particularly those stores
OL,9,Fregularly targeted by repeat
OL,10,Foffenders, and we fully understand the
OL,11,Fimpact and frustration on businesses,
OL,12,Fit's a crime which can affect
OL,13,Flivelihoods.
OL,15,F"Our local teams - across
OL,16,Finvestigations, neighbourhood and
OL,17,Fresponse - work together to prevent
OL,18,Fand tackle crimes which impact on our
OL,19,Fcommunities.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
