OL,3,CStore owner speaks out after 30%
OL,4,Cincrease in shoplifting in the West
OL,5,CMidlands
OL,7,F"Using local officer knowledge and
OL,8,Fworking with store security, we are
OL,9,Fable to identify suspects, and any
OL,10,Femerging trends or hotspots quicker.
OL,12,F"We routinely carry out regular high
OL,13,Fvisibility patrols in retail areas,
OL,14,Falong with other activity, to trace
OL,15,Fand catch offenders."
