OL,5,CMidlands
OL,7,FShe continued: "We work alongside
OL,8,Fnumerous Business Watch schemes across
OL,9,Fthe West Midlands, these are made up
OL,10,Fof representatives from local
OL,11,Fcompanies who come together to talk
OL,12,Fabout how they can support each other
OL,13,Fto boost their trade and benefit the
OL,14,Fcommunity and, where appropriate, work
OL,15,Fwith local police and other agencies
OL,16,Flike the council and local Business
OL,17,FImprovement District."
